title: Kardashians Private Jet searched by immigration officers after family speaks out
text: Now the first family of reality are being hit by Trump's travel ban chaos! Kardashians private jet is searched by immigration officers at LA airport amid heightened visa checks across the country Kim Kardashian West’s private jet has been searched by officials at LA Airport Move comes just days after Donald Trump imposed his ‘Muslim travel ban’ Kim and her family were returning from a four-day trip to Costa Rica on Tuesday The Kardashians' jet was boarded by customs and immigration officials After being interviewed by officials, Kim and her family were allowed to leave Just days earlier, Kim and Khloe had responded to Trump's 'Muslim ban' Kim tweeted statistics of numbers of Americans killed by Islamic immigrants Her sister wrote that: 'All of this in the news today breaks my heart' Published: 07:22 GMT, 1 February 2017 | Updated: 09:51 GMT, 1 February 2017 35 shares
